  name: "Adamantine Monk"
  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 9th level, a monk of the iron mountain has muscles so strong and\
    \ skin so resilient that he gains DR 1/--. This DR increases by 1 for every three\
    \ levels thereafter. As a swift action, the monk can spend 1 ki point to double\
    \ his DR until the beginning of his next turn.\nThis ability replaces improved\
    \ evasion."
